com.ibm.team.process.common

Interface ITeamArea

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, IAuditable, IAuditableHandle, IItem, IItemHandle, IManagedItem, IManagedItemHandle, INamed, IProcessArea, IProcessAreaHandle, IProcessContainer, IProcessContainerHandle, IProcessItem, IProcessItemHandle, ITeamAreaHandle

    public interface ITeamArea
extends ITeamAreaHandle, IProcessArea
    A team area defines the resort of a team inside a project area. The team process governing the project area also governs the team area. However, when the team process allows it, the team can customize the team process to its specific needs inside its team area.
    Since:
    0.5
